    "asOf": "2005-04-12",
    "date": "2005-04-28T18:18:08Z",
    "text": "Disaster Relief Equity Act of 2005 - Amends the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act to state that the religious status of a private nonprofit facility, or of the owner or operator of such a facility, shall not preclude its eligibility for Federal contributions to repair, restore, reconstruct, or replace the facility following damage or destruction by a major disaster."
